The evidence with the title 'Transcript and analysis: president Trump's speech to Congress ... ' says Feb 28, 2017  ... In the months leading up to the election , Trump began asking the rhetorical question to black voters — in front of overwhelmingly white audiences — “ what the hell do you have to lose ? ” He painted a picture of black neighborhoods as wracked with poverty , crime and schools that are “ no good, ” as he put it. 
